article_id:45,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding the Event's Daily Battle Not Resetting [Update],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue in the event Trick or Treasure!, taking place since <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539756000"></span>, where the daily battle Nightly Haunts is not resetting properly.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue. Any further updates regarding this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539950400"></span>]</strong></span><br>The following issue has been fixed.<br><br>■Details of the issue<br>After playing the daily battle &quot;Nightly Haunts&quot; from the event &quot;Trick or Treasure&quot; between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539810000"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539842399"></span>, it did not reset properly at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539842400"></span>.<br><br>This issue has been fixed so that the daily battle resets at the appropriate time.<br>We sent the following gifts to affected players:<br><br>・ Tricker Treats x300<br>・ Snack-o&rsquo;-Lanterns x50<br>・ Jack Chocolates x15<br><br>The gifts above have been sent to players who could not play the daily battle &quot;Nightly Haunts&quot; between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539919800"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539928799"></span> while this technical issue was taking place.<br><br>We also sent the following gift as a token of appreciation for your patience.<br><br>・ Quality Honey x1<br><br>The gift above was sent to all players who played the daily battle &quot;Nightly Haunts&quot; between <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539810000"></span> and <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1539842399"></span>.<br><br>You can check how many Tricker Treats you have after receiving the gifts using either of the methods below.<br><br>▼Method 1<br>1. Tap &quot;Home&quot; at the bottom of the screen.<br>2. Tap the &quot;Trick or Treasure!&quot; event banner on the home screen.<br>3. Tap the &quot;Tricker Treat Rewards&quot; button on the event screen.<br>・ Tricker Treats received will be added to the amount indicated under &quot;Total Obtained.&quot;<br>・ If the &ldquo;Total Obtained&rdquo; after receiving the gift is enough to unlock a Tricker Treat Reward, that reward will be earned automatically<br><br>▼Method 2<br>1. Tap &quot;Home&quot; at the bottom of the screen.<br>2. Tap the &quot;Trick or Treasure!&quot; event banner on the home screen.<br>3. Tap &quot;View Quests&quot; on the event screen.<br>4. Clear any of the event quests.<br>・ Tricker Treats received will be added to the amount indicated under &quot;Total Obtained&quot; on the results screen.<br>・ If the &ldquo;Total Obtained&rdquo; after receiving the gift is enough to unlock a Tricker Treat Reward, that reward will be earned automatically<br><br>■Notes<br>Items sent as gifts can be received from your goodie box.<br>Gifts can be picked up until <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1540533599"></span>.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1539867000,update_time1540539100